-We use mysql as the database.
-information for the msql database: 
            driver class.
            connetion url.
            username.
            password.
-the driver class for mysql database is com.mysql.jdbc.Driver.
-the connection url for the mysql database is jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/School.
-Where the  jdbc is the API,
-mysql is the use ip address, 
-3306 is the port  number and school is the database name.
-We may use any database in such,
-school  with our database name.
-the default username for the mysql database is root.
-It is the password given by the user at the time of installing the mysql database,
